quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  43,68,"(Zvichanzi kune avo vaitenda): Vanamati vangu! Hapana kutya kuchave kwamuri zuva ranhasi, kana kuti kusuruvara"
  43,69,Avo vaitenda muzviratidzo zvedu uye vaive vakazvipira kuna Allah (maMuslim)
  43,70,Pindai muParadhiso imi nevakadzi venyu murufaro
  43,71,"Matireyi egoridhe nemakomichi achatenderedzwa mavari. Mariri (Paradhiso) muchange muine zvinoshuvirwa nemoyo yavo, neizvo meso anoyevedzwa nazvo, uye vachagaramo zvachose"
  43,72,Iri ndiro Paradhiso ramagadzwa nhaka nekuda kwemabasa enyu amaiita (pahupenyu hwepanyika)
  43,73,Mariri (Paradhiso) kwamuri muchange muine michero yakawanda yamuchange muchidya (sezvamunoshuvira)
  43,74,"Zvirokwazo, maMujrimoon (vatadzi) vachange vari mumarwadzo ekumoto umo mavachagara zvachose"
  43,75,"Marwadzo haazomborerutswi kwavari, uye vachakandwa mumatambudziko vaine kudemba kwakanyanya, uye vaine kushushikana mariri"
  43,76,"Hatina kuva tinovakanganisira, asi (kuti) ivo pachavo vaiva vatadzi"
  43,77,"Uye vachachema: “Iwe Malik (muchengetedzi weGehena)! Ita kuti Tenzi vako vatipedzise (vatiuraye).” Achati: “Zvirokwazvo, muchagaramo zvachose.”"
  43,78,"Zvirokwazvo, taunza chokwadi (Muhammad (SAW) neQur’aan) kwamuri, asi vazhinji venyu vanovenga chokwadi"
  43,79,Kana kuti vakaronga urongwa? Naizvozvo nesuwo tiri kuronga
  43,80,"Kana kuti vanofunga here kuti hatinzwi zvakavandika zvavo uye zvavanoutaura muchivande? Hongu (tinozinzwa), uye vatumwa vedu (ngirozi) vanawo, vachinyora"
  43,81,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Kana vane nyasha dzose (Allah) vaine mwana (kana vana sezvamunotaura), naizvozvo ndiri wekutanga weavo vanomunamata (kuramba zvamunotaura, uye kutenda kuti Allah vari vega uye havana vana).”"
  43,82,"Kukudzwa kwose ngakuve kuna Tenzi vematenga nenyika, Tenzi vechigaro chepamusoro-soro. Kurumbidzwa kwose ngakuve kwavari pane zvose zvavanovasanganisa navo"
  43,83,Saka vasiyei vachitaura zvisina maturo uye vachitamba kusvikira vasangana nezuva ravo iro ravakavimbiswa
  43,84,"Ndivo (Allah) vanova vamwechete Ilaah (Mwari vanofanirwa kunamatwa) kudenga, vanova zvakare Ilaah (Mwari vanofanirwa kunamatwa) panyika. Ndivo vazere neungwaru, muzivi wezvose"
  43,85,"Makomborero ndeavo, muridzi weumambo hwekudenga nepasi, nezvose zviri pakati pawo, uye kwavari ndiko kune ruzivo rwenguva, uye kwavari muchadzoserwa (mese)"
  43,86,"Uye avo vavanodana kunze kwavo (Allah) havana masimba ekumiririra – kusara kweavo vanopa uchapupu pachokwadi (vanotenda muhumwechete hwaAllah uye vachiteerera mirairo yavo), uye vanoziva (humwechete hwaAllah)"
  43,87,"Asi kana ukavabvunza kuti ndiani akavasika, muzvokwadi vanoti: “Allah.” Saka vanofuratira sei (mukunamata Allah vakavasika)"
  43,88,"(Uye Allah vane ruzivo) rwe (Mashoko aMuhammad (SAW)) anoti: “Tenzi wangu! Zvirokwazvo, ava vanhu vasingatendi!”"
  43,89,"Saka vafuratire (Muhammad (SAW)) uye oti: Salaam (Runyararo)! Asi vachazviziva"